OCM:Add the ability to specify name of a Collection Element through XML Mapping files.Collection elements get mapped to a node "collection-element" when the mappings are specified through XML config files.  We need the ability to control this name through configuration.  Without that feature querying object structures is painful.  For example I have structure as below :

class Foo{
String id;
