TCK: NodeTest#testAddNodeItemExistsException fails if validation deferred until saveThe test expects addNode to fail if a same-name sibling already exists.  JSR-170 allows this validation to be deferred until save.

Proposal: call save in the "try" block.

--- NodeTest.java       (revision 422074)
+++ NodeTest.java       (working copy)
@@ -380,6 +391,7 @@
         try {
             // try to add a node with same name again
             defaultTestNode.addNode(nodeName3, testNodeType);
